*   [Erich Wolfgang Korngold](/Erich_Wolfgang_Korngold) (1897–1957), composer and conductor.
*   [Bohumil Hrabal](/Bohumil_Hrabal) (1914–1997), acclaimed author.
*   [Vítězslava Kaprálová](/V%C3%ADt%C4%9Bzslava_Kapr%C3%A1lov%C3%A1) (1915–1940), composer and conductor.
