**Nearby Cities**

Brno is strategically positioned within a network of major Central European cities. Prominent cities within a 300 km (186.41 mi) radius include [Prague](/Prague) (approx. 180 km), [Vienna](/Vienna) (approx. 110 km), and [Bratislava](/Bratislava) (approx. 125 km). Other significant urban centers within reach are [Dresden](/Dresden) (approx. 290 km), [Wrocław](/Wroc%C5%82aw) (approx. 210 km), [Katowice](/Katowice) (approx. 210 km), [Kraków](/Krak%C3%B3w) (approx. 260 km), and [Budapest](/Budapest) (approx. 260 km).

